Melody Patterson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Melody_Patterson 0 Melody Patricia Patterson (April 16, 1949 – August 20, 2015) was an American actress known for her role as Wrangler Jane in the 1960s television series F Troop and for her role as Ellie in the cult horror film Blood and Lace (1971).
